{"tid":1474746,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議記者朋友可以喺黑警記者會即場播片反駁佢地","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:39:04.000Z","uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"feed7f70b1757cb15294fee8b4e5c7abf592b628","tid":1474746,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"建議記者朋友可以喺黑警記者會即場播片反駁佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似頭先黑警記者會咁，個黑警話尋晚深水埗隻失控狗係用「合適語言」同市民溝通，其實可以帶定個pad即場播片反駁佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/366287960936354/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftang.earthquake%2Fvideos%2F366287960936354%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=f91dd03d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tang.earthquake/videos/366287960936354/</a><br />\n<br />\n一來，班黑警成日扮傻話自己冇資料冇睇過又唔知咩事，一播片佢就冇得避。<br />\n二來，未必個個市民都追得哂、睇齊咁多片，播咗可以等大家更清楚，好過就咁用口描述。<br />\n<br />\n上次print埋相出嚟其實係一個好好嘅做法，如果情況許可嘅話即場播埋片可能效果仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0388c879f3400f9e5af67f2ecb2a5fd6cf2f45a2","tid":1474746,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKtyThf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKtyThf.png&h=d5bda484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家佢地任講咁<br />\n橫掂佢地之前都係用laptop播"},{"pid":"a73810e0509b32936eb4fdb029d8465c3ec7874b","tid":1474746,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0388c879f3400f9e5af67f2ecb2a5fd6cf2f45a2","tid":1474746,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKtyThf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKtyThf.png&h=d5bda484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家佢地任講咁<br />\n橫掂佢地之前都